   - **TypeScript excess property check did not fire**: Predicted compilation error when passing `{ type: "sword", cursed: true }` literal to `Item = { type: string }`. Vitest/Vite transform doesn't enforce strict excess property checks, so test failed at runtime instead. Marked prediction as Incorrect.
